      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness compared to experimental measurements across 11 constructs from two independent laboratories. Mean absolute percentage error 4.7%; E/uval = 1.31, within the pre-established acceptance criterion of <1.96. Uncertainty quantification was performed using a Monte Carlo propagation of material property and geometry tolerances (1000 samples). We plan to extend with sensitivity analysis to rank the dominant input drivers in a future revision of this credibility package.",
