      "rationale": "Systematic mesh refinement study conducted across three mesh densities (coarse: ~120k elements, medium: ~340k elements, fine: ~890k elements). QoI changes between medium and fine meshes were <2.1% for stiffness, <1.8% for yield force, and <3.4% for force at 40 mm. Medium mesh adopted for production runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
