      "rationale": "Validation activities performed on the same non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design as the COU device, under the same ASTM F1717 loading protocol. Two-laboratory design increases confidence in reproducibility. The validation scenario is assessed as directly representative of the COU without extrapolation."
